	<p><span style="font-size: 22px;">The Massachusetts Medical
Society</span> is the statewide professional association for physicians 

and medical students. We are dedicated to educating and advocating for 

the patients and physicians of Massachusetts. We offer 
    <a href="/cme">online CME courses and live events</a> that award 

continuing medical education credits. The Society, under the auspices of 

NEJM Group, publishes the <em>New England Journal of Medicine,</em> a 

leading global medical journal and web site, and NEJM Journal Watch 

alerts and publications covering 13 specialties. </p>
</div>
